# Override the API base URL at build time.
#
# Leave commented out in local dev — Vite's proxy + the Cloudflare Worker's
# /api/* proxy both handle `/api/v1` same-origin.
#
# Set this only if you want the FE bundle to talk to a fully-absolute backend
# URL (e.g. when the FE and API live on different hosts and CORS is configured).
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://shipman-api.example.com/api/v1
